t orders from satisfied customers experiencing ongoing success with the products leads to higher Distributor incomes.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Herbalife pays Supervisors and above directly. The money you receive from royalties and bonuses is all yours &ndash; there&rsquo;s no need to cut&nbsp;<br />\r\n		checks back to people in your organization.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color:#428c36;\"><strong>Highly Effective, Science-based Products Developed to Meet Consumer Needs</strong></span><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Exclusive, high-demand products that have helped millions of people in more than 75 countries.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Satisfied customers provide referrals for results-based weight-management, nutrition and skincare products.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Herbalife is dedicated to developing innovative, effective products under the guidance of our Scientific Leadership, including&nbsp;<br />\r\n		Nobel* Laureate in Medicine Dr. Lou Ignarro, and with groundbreaking research at the Mark Hughes Cellular and Molecular Nutrition&nbsp;<br />\r\n		Laboratory at UCLA&dagger;.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color:#428c36;\"><strong>A World-class Company with Visionary Leadership to Support Your Business</strong></span><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Herbalife has grown consistently since 1980, and is still expanding.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Executives, Distributor leadership and employees are working to further the company&rsquo;s mission, vision and values, positioning the company&nbsp;<br />\r\n		for future growth.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Herbalife&rsquo;s mission for good nutrition, a healthy, active lifestyle and financial well-being helps millions of people reach their ideal weight, look and feel healthier, and earn what they&rsquo;re worth.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		We are listed on the prestigious New York Stock Exchange, are members of Direct Selling Associations around the world, and have brand visibility through sports sponsorships.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		We care: More than 60 Casa Herbalife programs on six continents provide better nutrition for children in need.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color:#428c36;\"><strong>Step-by-step Training Programs that Assist You in Starting Your Own Business and Expanding Locally,Nationally and Internationally</strong></span><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Training that supports growing your business through Distributor calls and events, along with advanced marketing materials and tools, including a helpful, easy-to-use Distributor website.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		An opportunity to take charge of your life by learning the skills that can help you run a successful and profitable business.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Simple, easy-to-duplicate business programs that are continually redeveloped and refined.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Support that requires the application of the highest standards of business ethics, conduct and accountability to all Herbalife Independent Distributors.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color:#428c36;\"><strong>Why Herbalife? Because we are committed to empowering you to live a healthier, financially prosperous life.</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n*The Nobel Foundation has no affiliation with Herbalife and does not review, approve or endorse Herbalife products.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&dagger;The University of California does not endorse specific products or services as a matter of policy.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&dagger;The University of California does not endorse specific products or services as a matter of policy. This section of the website advertises the results achieved by Herbalife Independent Distributors across a wide spectrum. These are examples and not necessarily typical or average,nor do they represent a guarantee of your personal results. Some examples are those of persons within the top 1% of all Distributors. As with any business opportunity,success depends largely on the individual distributor&#39;s skills, motivation and effort. For average financial performance data, see the Statement of Average Gross Compensation.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://opportunity.herbalife.com/Content/en-US/pdf/business-opportunity/statement_average_gross_usen.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Statement of Average Gross Compensation</strong></a><br />\r\n','tb_article_header','','','a_desc'),(56,'','tb_section','','','l_image'),(57,'Dream Team Sicence','tb_section','','','l_title'),(58,'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Yp50enYLrs','tb_section','','','l_link'),(59,'','tb_section','','','l_desc'),(60,'','tb_section','','','l_image'),(61,'Success stories(Weight Loss)','tb_section','','','l_title'),(62,'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7nLwon3mO5g','tb_section','','','l_link'),(63,'','tb_section','','','l_desc'),(64,'','tb_section','','','l_image'),(65,'','tb_article_header','','','a_desc'),(66,'','tb_article_header','','','a_desc'),(69,'PMT- Presentation Version','tb_menu','','','m_title'),(70,'PMT-Speed Version','tb_menu','','','m_title'),(71,'Niteworks – Simple','tb_menu','','','m_title'),(72,'Formula 1 Bars','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(73,'<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>Herbalife Formula 1 Express Bars:</strong> Perfect for when you&rsquo;re out and about or don&rsquo;t have time to make a smoothie. Herbalife&rsquo;s Formula 1 bars are packed with essential vitamins and minerals, with 207 calories per bar and all the benefits of a Formula 1 Shake.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(74,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(75,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(76,'<p>\r\n	Formula 1 Shakes is the preferred healthy meal solution for millions of people every day helping them achieve weight management results they feel proud of.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	When you&rsquo;re out and about, you&rsquo;ll never have to worry about missing a healthy meal&hellip;again! NEW Formula 1 Healthy Meal Bar is the convenient Healthy Meal on the go.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>ADVANTAGES</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&bull; Balanced essential nutrients for a complete healthy meal replacement<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&bull; High fibre and protein for sustained energy and to keep you fuller for longer<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&bull; 206/207 calories (by flavour)<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&bull; Low Gi<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&bull; Suitable for vegetarians<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&bull; Crunchy and chewy</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>#2669 - Chocolate</strong><br />\r\n	<strong>#2670 - Red Fruit and Yoghurt</strong></p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(77,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(78,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(79,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(80,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(81,'Formula 2','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(82,'Herbalife Formula 2: Herbalife&rsquo;s Multivitamin Complex contains essential vitamins and minerals to help you achieve your RDA.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(83,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(84,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(85,'<p>\r\n	<strong>Formula 2 Multivitamin, your daily multivitamin with over 15 vitamins and minerals to help you reach your RDA.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Helps you reach your daily vitamin and mineral needs, as part of a healthy, well balanced diet.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Vitamin A, folate, B6, B12 and zinc to help maintain the normal function of the immune system</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Calcium and phosphorous for the maintenance of normal bone health and teeth</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Vitamin C and E to help protect cells from oxidative stress</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	It&rsquo;s important to include varied and balanced meals as part of your daily diet. However, when your lifestyle is hectic and your finding it hard to get the balance right, support your body with F2 Multivitamin Complex to provide the essential vitamins and minerals your body needs.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	One tablet three times daily with meals. This product can be used in conjunction with Herbalife Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>#3122</strong></p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(86,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(87,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(88,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(89,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(90,'Fibre & Herb','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(91,'Fibre &amp; Herb can help you increase your daily fibre intake.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(92,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(93,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(94,'<p>\r\n	<strong>Fibre &amp; Herb contains oat fibre together with parsley, orange blossom, hibiscus flower and fennel seed powder.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Fibre supplement to help you reach the recommended daily fibre intake of 25g per day.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Ideal to use in conjunction with Herbalife Formula 1 shakes and Formula 2 Multivitamin Complex as part of your weight management programme.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Eating a balanced diet with plenty of wholegrains can help you meet you daily fibre requirements. If you are struggling to eat enough fibre, taking a fibre supplement can help you to reach the recommended daily fibre intake of 25g per day.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Take two tablets with each meal, three times per day.<br />\r\n	This product may be used in conjunction with Herbalife Formula 1 Nutritional Shake Mix and Herbalife Formula 2 Multivitamin Complex.</p>\r\n<strong>#3114</strong>','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(95,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(96,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(97,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(98,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(99,'formula 1','tb_section','','','l_title'),(100,'','tb_section','','','l_link'),(101,'','tb_section','','','l_desc'),(102,'9b8dfa55c080f11d91fb26ef32fefc46.jpg','tb_section','','','l_image'),(103,'formula 1 bars','tb_section','','','l_title'),(104,'','tb_section','','','l_link'),(105,'','tb_section','','','l_desc'),(106,'2eddc7a477c8c7cadec29f43138bb86b.jpg','tb_section','','','l_image'),(107,'Liftoff®','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(108,'<strong>Herbalife</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Liftoff&reg;</strong> low calorie effervescent energy drink for anytime anywhere.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(109,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(110,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(111,'<p>\r\n	<strong>When you&rsquo;re feeling tired, re-energise with Liftoff, a caffeinated low calorie, effervescent energy drink. Caffeine helps to increase alertness and improve concentration.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		10 kcal per serving, a great replacement for fizzy sugary drinks</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		100% of your Vitamin C RDA to help alleviate tiredness and fatigue</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		100% of your B vitamins (B1, B2, B3, B5, B6, Biotin) RDA for normal energy metabolism</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Contains natural caffeine from Guarana and caffeine powder</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Every serving provides 75 mg of caffeine, to help increase alertness and improve concentration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Stress and tiredness often cause us to reach for sugary, high calorie foods and drink. Hydrate and give your body an energising lift with LiftOff, a low calorie energy drink with 100% of your RDA of vitamins B (B1, B2, B3, Panthothenic Acid, B6, Biotin) &amp; C.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Take one to two tablets each day by dissolving them with water.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	#3152 <strong>Lemon-Lime</strong><br />\r\n	#3151 <strong>Orange</strong></p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(112,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(113,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(114,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(115,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(116,'QuickSpark','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(117,'Herbalife QuickSpark lozenges are caffeine-free, sugar-free and calorie-free.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(118,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(119,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(120,'<p>\r\n	<strong>Leading a busy life, or travelling often can sometimes mean trying to operate when you&rsquo;re feeling less than your best. If you need refreshment during the day, try QuickSpark.<br />\r\n	Nicotinamide adenine dinucleotide (NADH) occurs naturally in the body and is involved in energy metabolism.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Non caffeinated dissolvable lozenge</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Sugar and calorie-free</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		No artificial colours or flavours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	QuickSpark delivers non caffeinated refreshment with 10 mg of CoEnzyme 1 in a convenient dissolvable lozenge.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Take 1 lozenge per day as needed. Place under tongue until fully dissolved. For maximum effectiveness do not chew lozenge.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HEALTH FACT:</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Nicotinamide adenine dinucleotide (NADH) occurs naturally in the body and is involved in energy metabolism.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Key Benefits</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Contains a patented formula of CoEnzyme 1, which plays an important role in producing natural energy at a cellular level</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		CoEnzyme 1, has crucial roles in many cellular processes.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Fast acting: lozenge dissolves quickly and easily</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		No caffeine, no sugar, no calories. No artificial colours or flavours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>WHY DO YOU NEED IT?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Your body has naturally occurring levels of CoEnzyme 1. With age our levels of CoEnzyme 1 declines and as a result our body&rsquo;s energy levels decline. Because CoEnzyme 1 is used to generate ATP energy, the more CoEnzyme 1 the body has, the more ATP energy can be made by each cell to function properly.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Take 1 lozenge per day as needed. Place under tongue until fully dissolved. For maximum effectiveness do not chew lozenge.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	*ATP (Adenosine Triphosphate) is the body&rsquo;s main source of cellular energy.</p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(121,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(122,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(123,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(124,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(125,'H3O Pro','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(126,'<strong>Herbalife H30 Pro</strong> carbohydrate-electrolyte drink is ideal to drink before, during and after exerise.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(127,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(128,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(129,'<p>\r\n	<strong>H&sup3;O Pro&trade; is a carbohydrate-electrolyte drink, designed to be taken before, during or after exercise. With an osmolality of 280-300 osmol/kg &ndash; it&rsquo;s ideal for sports performance.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Developed by experts in sports nutrition, H&sup3;O Pro&trade; is ideal to drink before, during and after exercise for hydration:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Provides 137 kcal per serving</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Provides an osmolality of 280-300 mOsmol/kg &ndash; ideal for sports performance</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Provides Vitamins E and C which help protect cells against oxidative stress</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Contains no artificial sweeteners, flavours or preservatives</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Maintaining hydration and energy levels during sports or exercise is vital. Drinking water alone may not be enough as it does not typically contain electrolytes or carbohydrates. Before, during and after exercise, fuel your body with the right balance of electrolytes and carbohydrates.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>DID YOU KNOW?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	As little as 2% fluid loss during exercise or mild dehydration can significantly affect performance.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	One serving (1 sachet diluted with 500ml of water) is recommended for every 60 minutes of intense exercise where you sweat heavily. For average, serious and pro athletes: take one serving before and/or during training to keep you hydrated.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>#2646</strong></p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(130,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(131,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(132,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(133,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(134,'N-R-G','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(135,'<strong>Herbalife N-R-G</strong> Nature&#39;s Raw Guarana contains guarana with orange pekoe, a traditional black tea.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(136,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(137,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(138,'<p>\r\n	<strong>NRG tablets contain caffeine from guarana to help support alertness and helps reduce the feeling of mental fatigue.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Guarana, blended with orange pekoe, a traditional black tea with a fine and rich flavour</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Contains 32 mg of caffeine from Guarana.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Throughout the day, there may be times when you feel like you just can&rsquo;t concentrate anymore. When mental fatigue sets in, it can be challenging to stay alert and focused. Supplementing with guarana may be a good option to help keep you focused and energised.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Take two to four tablets each day.<br />\r\n	Guarana is a shrub native to South America, it has been used for centuries by Amazon Indians for its caffeine content.</p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(139,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(140,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(141,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(142,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(143,'Niteworks','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(144,'<strong>Herbalife Niteworks</strong> is a night-time food supplement with L-Arginine and L-Citruline plus vitamins C and E and folic acid.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(145,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(146,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(147,'<p>\r\n	<strong>Niteworks is a night-time food supplement with L-Argine, L-Citruline and Vitamins C &amp; E and Folic Acid.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Niteworks contains the amino acids L-Arginine and L-Citruline</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		High in folic acid</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		High in vitamins C and E to protect the cells from oxidative stress</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		With lemon balm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Nitric Oxide is a naturally occurring gas in the body that promotes normal blood and vascular circulation, when combined with a balanced and varied diet, and exercise.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Mix two scoops (9g) of Niteworks&reg; powder with 250ml of water or juice. Drink at night before bedtime. Niteworks&reg; is night-time nutrition particularly designed for anyone but especially for those above the age of 30.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>#3150</strong></p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(148,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(149,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(150,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(151,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(152,'Herbalifeline','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(153,'<strong>Herbalifeline</strong>&nbsp;is a daily omega 3 supplement, rich in EPA and DHA to help support heart health, as part of a balanced diet.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(154,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(155,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(156,'<p>\r\n	<strong>Herbalifeline&reg; is an omega 3 supplement rich in Omega-3 essential fatty-acids EPA and DHA, known to help maintain a healthy heart.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Rich in EPA and DHA to help maintain a healthy heart. To achieve this beneficial effect, consume 250 mg of EPA &amp; DHA per day as recommended by the European Food Safety Authority (EFSA)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Consuming Omega 3 fatty acids helps keep your heart healthy, our bodies do not produce adequate levels so we need to obtain them from an external source</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		DHA also contributes to the maintenance of normal brain function and vision</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Contains essential oils to freshen the taste</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Studies have shown many western diets are very low in the long chain omega-3 fatty acids (EPA &amp; DHA), which is why a supplement may be beneficial. Nutritionists&rsquo; advice is for people to consume between 2 and 3 servings of fish per week to achieve the recommended omega-3 intake.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Take 1-3 capsules three times a day preferably with meals.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>#0065</strong></p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(157,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(158,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(159,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(160,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(161,'RoseOx','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(162,'<strong>Herbalife RoseOx</strong> is a well-rounded food supplement with Rosemary and other botanical ingredients.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(163,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(164,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(165,'<p>\r\n	<strong>RoseOx is a well rounded food supplement containing botanical extracts including rosemary, turmeric and cruciferous vegetables.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		When life is busy and hectic, RoseOx can help give your body the support it needs to cope.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	If you&rsquo;re struggling to cope, RoseOx is specially formulated to support your body during tense times.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Take one tablet a day, preferably with meals.</p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(166,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(167,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(168,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(169,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(170,'Xtra-Cal','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(171,'<strong>Herbalife Xtra-Cal</strong> calcium supplement with added vitamin D3 and magnesium helps to support strong bones and teeth.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(172,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(173,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(174,'<p>\r\n	<strong>Xtra-Cal is a daily calcium supplement, providing over 100% of your RDA of calcium required for the maintenance of healthy bones and teeth.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Helps maintain healthy bones and teeth</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Contains over 100% of your calcium RDA per serving</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Rich in vitamin D, essential for calcium absorption and needed for proper muscle function</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Also contains magnesium, copper, manganese and zinc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Your daily calcium requirement depends on your age and a variety of other factors. For example, teens need more calcium than adults. Older adults, particularly post menopausal women, need extra calcium to help prevent osteoporosis.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>DID YOU KNOW?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Milk provides a range of essential nutrients but to put things practically, a daily serving of Xtra-Cal provides you with 850 mg of calcium which is similar to the calcium provided by three glasses of milk.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>#0020</strong></p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(175,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(176,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(177,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(178,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(179,'Florafibre','tb_product','','','pro_name'),(180,'<strong>Herbalife Florafibre</strong>&nbsp;is a unique food supplement which contributes to your daily intake of fibre.','tb_product','','','pro_desc'),(181,'','tb_product','','','pro_color'),(182,'','tb_product','','','pro_material'),(183,'<p>\r\n	<strong>Florafibre is a unique food supplement which contributes to your daily intake of fibre.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>KEY BENEFITS</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Contributes to your daily intake of fibre</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		A daily serving provides 22% of the recommended amount of fibre for adults</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>HOW CAN IT HELP YOU?</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Fibre is known to keep the digestive tract healthy by providing bulk and decreasing the transit time in the gut. Research has shown that many people do not reach the recommended daily fibre intake of 25g a day. A fibre supplement along with healthy sources of fibre such as fruit, vegetables and wholegrain foods can help to increase your fibre intake.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>USAGE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Take one to three tablets, three times per day.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>#0023</strong></p>\r\n','tb_product','','','pro_remarks'),(184,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_title'),(185,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_keyword'),(186,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_description'),(187,'','tb_product','','','pro_seo_link_keyword'),(188,'','tb_product_cat','','','cat_url'),(189,'NouriFusion®','tb_product_cat','','','cat_name'),(190,'