ese Mine has commenced production in the mid of 2013. Production is expected to reach the peak within three to four years of the mine firing up its first drills, as more of its operations move underground. The target is to produce 2.5 million tonnes of manganese ore annually.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn addition to the mine itself, the Kudumane complex will also operate crushing and screening plant, provide storage facilities to handle the mine&rsquo;s residue and various support infrastructure. Plans are also afoot to construct a sintering plant, which will allow the mine to ship out its ore after undergoing the pre-smelting process.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor more details, please visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.kmr.co.za/\" target=\"new\">http://www.kmr.co.za</a>.','tb_article_details','除了矿山本身之外，Kudumane的配套工程还将进行粉碎和筛选工厂的运作，提供存储设施来处理矿山废料及各种支持性设施。规划还正在建造一座烧结工厂，使得矿石可以接受冶炼前处理过程然后再运出去。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n更多信息，请浏览网站<a href=\"http://www.kmr.co.za/\" target=\"new\">http://www.kmr.co.za</a>','','b_desc1'),(430,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(431,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(806,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(807,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(808,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption3'),(809,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption4'),(810,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(811,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(812,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(639,'<br />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 微軟正黑體, \'Microsoft JhengHei\', 蘋果儷中黑, \'Apple LiGothic Medium\', 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">Mining Operations</strong>','tb_article_details','<br />\r\n<strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, sans-serif, 微軟正黑體, \'Microsoft JhengHei\', 蘋果儷中黑, \'Apple LiGothic Medium\', 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">Mining Operations</strong>','','b_desc1'),(640,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(641,'','tb_ar