ules and INCOTERMS is preferred, but it is not a must;</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Attentive to details, mature, independent, able to meet tight deadlines, good team player and has problem solving skills</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Proficient in PC skills (Microsoft Word and Excel) is a must; and</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Proficient in both spoken and written English and Mandarin is a must.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nWe offer good opportunities and competitive compensation package including 5-days work, general holidays and performance bonus to the successful candidate.&nbsp; Interested parties please send a detailed resume with current and expected salary and date of availability to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:hongkong@asia-minerals.com\">hongkong@asia-minerals.com</a>.&nbsp; For further information of our company, please visit our website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.asia-minerals.com/\">http://www.asia-minerals.com</a>.&nbsp; Information provided will be kept confidential and will only be used for the recruitment related purpose.','','l_desc'),(662,'','tb_section','','','l_image'),(396,'Introduction','tb_article_header','Introduction','','a_title'),(397,'','tb_article_header','','','a_desc'),(398,'<img img=\"\" src=\"/cms/upload/aml/article/b_19_2.jpg?rand=990133881\" />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>Kudumane Manganese Resources (Proprietary) Ltd. (</strong>abbreviated as <strong>&ldquo;KMR&rdquo; </strong>hereafter<strong>)</strong> is a manganese mining company duly registered and incorporated in accordance with the laws of South Africa.</p>\r\n<br />\r\nKMR&rsquo;s headquarters is located in Johannesburg and it operates a manganese mine (&ldquo;<strong>Kudumane Manganese Mine</strong>&rdquo;) in the Northern Cape province around 80km northwest of Kuruman in South Africa.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAsia Minerals Limited via intermediate holding companies is a major shareholder in KMR and plays a significant role as a technical and marketing services provider to KMR. Bold Moves 1715 (Propriety) Limited and Afris Manganese (Pty) Ltd are the two BEE entity partners.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe mining operation will consist of a combination of open pits and underground mining. We target that an initial 1.5 million tonnes of manganese ore per year will be exported by both road and rail to other countries through Port Elizabeth and Durban. Once the Coega Industrial Development Zone and Deepwater Port opens up, they will be the preferred exit point for the mine&rsquo;s product.','tb_article_details','<img img=\"\" src=\"/cms/upload/aml/article/b_19_2.jpg?rand=990133881\" />\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>酷都锰矿资源公司</strong>(此后缩写为&nbsp;&ldquo;<strong>KMR</strong>&rdquo;&nbsp;)是一家依照南非法律合法注册并成立的锰矿开采公司。<br />\r\n	&nbsp;<br />\r\n	KMR的总部位于南非的约翰内斯堡，所运作的锰矿(&ldquo;<strong>Kudumane</strong><strong>锰矿</strong>&rdquo;)在南非的北开普省，位于南非库鲁曼西北大约80公里处。<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	亚洲矿业有限公司作为中间持股公司，是KMR的一个主要股东，同时也充当KMR的技术和市场服务的重要提供者。Bold Moves 1715 (Propriety) Limited 及Afris Manganese (Pty) Ltd是两家&ldquo;黑人经济振兴法案&rdquo;实体合作伙伴。<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	矿山的运作由露天矿厂和地下开采两部分组成。我们的目的是起初每年150万吨的锰矿通过公路运输及铁路运输经由南非伊丽莎白港和德班港出口至其他国家。一旦库哈工业发展区还有深水港开启，我们会考虑优先将这里作为矿石的出口港。<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	锰矿已经于2013年年中开始生产。随着更多的开采转入地下，生产预期会自矿山开钻起3至4年内达到顶峰。目标为每年生产2.5万吨锰矿。</p>\r\n','','b_desc1'),(486,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(487,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(828,'Logistics Officer','tb_section','Logistics Officer','','l_title'),(795,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(796,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(797,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(798,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption3'),(799,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption4'),(488,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(489,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption3'),(490,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption4'),(491,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(492,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(493,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(494,'','tb_article_detai