 supported by the well ‐ facilitated transportation system, including good railway and highway network.</p>\r\n','','b_desc1'),(543,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(544,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(545,'<h2>\r\n	Location</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	IMA is located about 900 kilometers away from one of the largest seaports in China &ndash; Tianjin port.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	IMA is fully supported by the well-facilitated transportation system, including good railway and highway network.</p>\r\n','tb_article_details','<h2>\r\n	Location</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	IMA is located about 900 kilometers away from one of the largest seaports in China &ndash; Tianjin port.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	IMA is fully supported by the well-facilitated transportation system, including good railway and highway network.</p>\r\n','','b_desc1'),(546,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(547,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(553,'<h2>\r\n	Production</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	IMA has three 12,500 KVA electric arc furnaces for producing Silicon Manganese and one 3,500 KVA refinery furnace for producing Medium and Low Carbon Ferromanganese</p>\r\n','tb_article_details','<h2>\r\n	Production</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	IMA has three 12,500 KVA electric arc furnaces for producing Silicon Manganese and one 3,500 KVA refinery furnace for producing Medium and Low Carbon Ferromanganese</p>\r\n','','b_desc1'),(554,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(555,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(583,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(576,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption4'),(575,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption3'),(574,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(573,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(572,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(562,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(563,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(564,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(565,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption3'),(566,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption4'),(567,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(568,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(569,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(570,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption3'),(571,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption4'),(582,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(581,'<h2>\r\n	Production</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	A high degree of flexibility in design and structure allows IMA to produce a wide range of Manganese Ferroalloys. IMA currently has three 12,500KVA electric arc furnaces for producing Silicon Manganese and one 3,500KVA refinery furnace for producing Medium and Low Carbon Ferromanganese. IMA&rsquo;s current production capacity is about 90,000MT per year.</p>\r\n','tb_article_details','<h2>\r\n	<strong>生产</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">由于工厂及炉台设计上及结构上高度灵活性，IMA可以生产出品种范围广的锰铁合金产品。IMA目前拥有3台12,500KVA用来生产硅锰合金的电弧炉，及一台3,500KVA用来生产中、低碳锰铁的精炼炉。IMA目前的产能为每年90,000吨。</span></h2>\r\n','','b_desc1'),(579,'Introduction','tb_article_header','Introduction','','a_title'),(580,'','tb_article_header','','','a_desc'),(597,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(596,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(595,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(587,'<h2>\r\n	IMA Resource Ltd.</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	IMA Resource Ltd. (Herein as &ldquo;IMA&rdquo;) is the first Manganese smelting plant of AML. It was acquired in 2004. IMA is located in Inner Mongolia, China, where there are abundant resources of coal for coke and power generation that gives advantage for the smelting business as with competitive power costs.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"imgfloat\" style=\"font-size: 12px; float: left;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/en/images/IMA/1.png\" style=\"font-size: 12px; width: 850px;\" />\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"/en/images/IMA/2.png\" style=\"font-size: 12px; width: 850px;\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','tb_article_details','<h2>\r\n	<strong>内蒙古亚矿资源有限公司</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">内蒙古亚矿资源有限公司 (简称&ldquo;IMA&rdquo;) 是亚矿所拥有的第一家锰冶炼厂。此工厂于2004年被收购。IMA坐落于中国的内蒙古自治区，那里蕴藏着丰富的煤炭资源，而且低电价也给冶炼创造了一定的优势。</span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div class=\"imgfloat\" style=\"font-size: 12px; float: left;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/en/images/IMA/1.png\" style=\"font-size: 12px; width: 850px;\" />\r\n	<p>\r\n		<img src=\"/en/images/IMA/2.png\" style=\"font-size: 12px; width: 850px;\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n','','b_desc1'),(418,'News','tb_article_header','News','','a_title'),(419,'','tb_article_header','','','a_desc'),(601,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(602,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(721,'<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><u><strong>April 2014 Update</strong></u></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','tb_article_details','<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><u><strong>April 2014 Update</strong></u></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','','b_desc1'),(588,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(589,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(590,'','tb_article_details','','','b_desc1'),(591,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption1'),(592,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption2'),(593,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption3'),(594,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption4'),(598,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption3'),(599,'','tb_article_details','','','b_caption4'),(600,'<div 0=\"\" 10px=\"\" 10px0=\"\" 15px=\"\" class=\"imgfloat\" style=\"float: right; width: auto\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: 12px; \"><a class=\"fancyphoto\" href=\"/en/images/IMA/4.png\"> <img src=\"/en/images/IMA/location.png\" width=\"220px\" /> </a></span></div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Location</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	IMA is located about 900 kilometers away from one of the largest seaports of China &ndash; Tianjin port. The well-facilitated transportation system, including good railway and highway network, all the way through from the plant site till to the Tianjin port has given good support to IMA for the logistics.</p>\r\n','tb_article_details','<div 0=\"\" 10px=\"\" 10p